{
  "page": "Ice (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a></b> is the ancestral greatsword of House Stark.\n</p><p>It may also refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arson_Iceaxe\" title=\"Arson Iceaxe\">Arson Iceaxe</a>, a wildling raider</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_ice\" title=\"Battle in the ice\">Battle in the ice</a>, battle between Stannis Baratheon and the Bolton forces</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bay_of_Ice\" title=\"Bay of Ice\">Bay of Ice</a>, a large bay along the shores of northwestern Westeros</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark_(Ice_Eyes)\" title=\"Brandon Stark (Ice Eyes)\">Brandon Stark</a>, also known as <i>Ice Eyes</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Giant_ice_spider\" title=\"Giant ice spider\">Giant ice spider</a>, a legendary species of animal</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ice_cell\" title=\"Ice cell\">Ice cell</a>, rooms carved from the base of the Wall</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ice-river_clans\" title=\"Ice-river clans\">Ice-river clans</a>, clans of free folk</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Ice_Wolf\" title=\"Ice Wolf\">Ice Wolf</a></i>, a ship captained by Corlys Velaryon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_song_of_ice_and_fire\" title=\"The song of ice and fire\">The song of ice and fire</a>, a subject of a prophecy</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ice_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>George R. R. Martin's and derived works:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Calendar\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar\">A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Campaign_Guide\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide\">A Song of Ice and Fire Campaign Guide</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Roleplaying\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying\">A Song of Ice and Fire Roleplaying</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire:_Tactics\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics\">A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Art_of_George_R._R._Martin%27s_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Art of George R. R. Martin&#39;s A Song of Ice and Fire\">The Art of George R. R. Martin's A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Ice_Dragon\" title=\"The Ice Dragon\">The Ice Dragon</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405140500\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:37662-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405140500 and revision id 311279\n -->\n",
